{"tid":2274313,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Terry: 引發黃圈內鬥後 藍營計劃邊緣化侵侵支持者","createTime":"2020-11-06T10:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T13:22:47.000Z","uid":48083,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2cafa17bcfbc413da9c31c052dadf31ea48c5e04","tid":2274313,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:54:53.000Z","msg":"借你三分鐘，這篇很重要。請細閱<br />\n並廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n今天的內鬥，完全有跡可尋，十分危險。<br />\n<br />\n因為美國大選，香港的社交平台出現了極多爭端。並非黃藍爭論，而是黃營之間的互相批評。<br />\n<br />\n首先，不能把所有責任推給網軍。假帳號是有用的，但只得假帳號，是搞不出風潮。需要有真人配合，而我們都是棋子。<br />\n<br />\n2016年，俄羅斯有一個由普京親自指揮的資訊戰中心，單的就是搞亂美國大選。除了駭進美國的選舉網絡，也派出了大量殭屍帳號，於社交媒體帶動風向。<br />\n<br />\n假帳號，大多數是人工智能，圍繞感敏議題，包括難民圍牆和黑人權益（也就是Black Lives Matter）等等。<br />\n<br />\n同樣在2016年，英國的脫歐公投亦在著網軍身影。有一批殭屍帳號極力推動英國人脫歐，在公投前幾日，甚至有超過三成的網上輿論，由不足1%的Twitter用戶主導。<br />\n<br />\n背後由誰操控？也是俄羅斯。<br />\n<br />\n無論美國大選，或是英國脫歐，對於民主選舉之兩極相爭的議題，俄國都極力將兩邊極端化。目的，就是讓美國陷入「極左 VS 極右」，英國變成「脫歐狂人 VS 留歐狂人」。<br />\n<br />\n邊緣化異見者，就能製造出更多異見者，和大大小小的同溫層。這就是社會撕裂，要修補，以年計甚至不可能。<br />\n<br />\n回到香港情況，中國肯定不想特朗普連任，也很清楚坊間的民意，很多抗爭者的相關態度，與「攬炒」同出一徹。<br />\n<br />\n過去一年，我們可以你建制媒體和名人的風向，清晰見到，「污名化攬炒」是共同任務。旨在打經濟民生牌，讓中間派或淺黃困於生活，然後民意逆轉。也方便將武肺帶來的破壞，全數推卸予抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n例如，國泰大裁員，官媒就定義為「香港攬炒」，現在大家都該懂了。<br />\n<br />\n把事情催化到極致，就會出現邊緣化。去年勇武抗爭抬頭，網上就有風向，非黑即白地將國際線、文宣和遊行當成「和理非無用」。當然全民勇武是一個出路，但過份壓制其他路線，就會讓勇武派成為邊緣化，變成更少的同溫層。<br />\n<br />\n不一定是網軍所為，事實上，前線當然都希望有更多人參與和支援。但發言者的身份在此並不重要，反而應該留意政府的反應。<br />\n<br />\n由反送中開始，港府一直都分開「和理非」與「勇武」兩派，每每強調暴力不可容易，但會聆聽和平民意。<br />\n<br />\n當然最後叫口宣一樣犯法，但章法一致，就是分化和勇。<br />\n<br />\n因為知道勇武的威脅，所以對藍營和國際線，醜化前線為「收錢做嘢」、「搞事分子」。而對黃營內部，以上基調講過不通，就全力將勇武派邊緣化。<br />\n<br />\n其實，對特朗普議題都一樣。無論有否網軍參與，由於香港抗爭者極度希望其連任，加強反華政策及制裁香港藍營。背後是疫情下的抗爭緩和，以及年半以來的情緒投射，這些民意是強大的。<br />\n<br />\n所以對特朗普不利的，例如叫人Fact Check假消息（雖然查證也不等於損害共和黨，但民粹如是），就會被部份網民炮轟是「中立派」、「收中共錢」、「鬼」和「親拜登」。<br />\n<br />\n這變成了互相邊際化的形勢，於是撐特普朗的又分成了兩派，而雙方都覺得對家走火入魔。<br />\n<br />\n或者你會問，這樣做對政府有什麼好處？<br />\n<br />\n其實，只要民間愈多對立，對真正抗爭對象的情緒就會緩和。而邊緣化不同派別，也更方便幕後人士出手帶動風向。<br />\n<br />\n2016年美國大選，跟據美國時任中央情報告局局長布倫南的線報，普京當期買希拉莉勝選，但網絡報署，卻是用大量殭屍盲撐右翼，激進化共和黨的形象變成「針對黑人、白人至上」。<br />\n<br />\n其後，據報普京兩邊押注，也賭特朗普會贏。但網軍的方針不變，因為美國愈亂，對俄方愈有利。而當時的美國總統奧馬巴明知俄方入侵了大選，卻沒有公開反擊，然後因為官僚主義等問題，一切到其卸任都仿佛沒有發生過。<br />\n<br />\n回到香港，把政府當成俄羅斯，現在明白為什麼他們會樂見，香港人因為美國大選鬧到面紅耳熱了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n藍營一直妖魔化特普朗，也宣揚中國強大。所以藍絲對於特朗普連任，很多都覺得等到美國會攬炒。對拜登更是講都講唔出印象。<br />\n<br />\n結果，因為特朗普而爭執最大的，是一班特朗普支持者。<br />\n<br />\n我們可以做的，是對意見不同，但方向一致的朋友，給予更多包容。對於即時的資訊，也留更多餘地，保持查證的態度。<br />\n<br />\n要講的講完了，對於坊間網民覺得我是「藍絲」和「收政府錢」，不作回應，明嘅就明。<br />\n<br />\n共勉豬。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.對於坊間指控，或這一篇再引來大量攻擊，我不會再回應。清者自ching，Thanks Ching。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;--------------------------<br />\n【Patreon：媒體研究懶人包】<br />\n帶你了解資訊戰，分析媒體亂局。<br />\n逢二、四、六更新，每周一Live，深度講媒體。文字、Podcast並行，深入淺出，希望各位G持：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/terrylazyclass\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fterrylazyclass&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9vzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=2a4beee1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/terrylazyclass</a><br />\n你的訂閱，可以支持更多資訊戰分析。"},{"pid":"ae89b369720588b0349acb8e33665103dea09482","tid":2274313,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c9177601cc99e9c1b3a6e0fd4e4255ddb00f9d9","tid":2274313,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:55:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6769ae601f964e1a73bb664d4fe58adf888304a","tid":2274313,"uid":286897,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a733cf87716853f20fa9b2f50833c1066bd37646","tid":2274313,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以罵還罵，玩到人身攻擊就一定五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b7adac38895cc00115037fad566ec5d8c82482","tid":2274313,"uid":121058,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"都on9既 依家係邊緣化緊認同民主黨/反侵既黃絲<br />\n成個時事台都係愛侵力<br />\n黃絲一定要支持侵？hocc唔係黃？"},{"pid":"216f3475107fc8e90521159e83591aad6b1287ca","tid":2274313,"uid":303110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22af61919df69582243406d511e71b82308ac66d","tid":2274313,"uid":215501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d2d8dbc7876c0d9860f51b384f2fe23f5f1878","tid":2274313,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c3391493a15d20c49d395cd07c372027f1d6701","tid":2274313,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86b7adac38895cc00115037fad566ec5d8c82482","tid":2274313,"uid":121058,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"都on9既 依家係邊緣化緊認同民主黨/反侵既黃絲<br />\n成個時事台都係愛侵力<br />\n黃絲一定要支持侵？hocc唔係黃？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被迫害妄想症"},{"pid":"a12213f587ca4eefd07f3397cdc5f6f7ebaa93d0","tid":2274313,"uid":128261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"其實留意香港政局夠耐，就會知黃圈內鬥係遲早既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連咁細既本土派都可以細胞分裂<br />\n一直以來只係靠抗爭熱度勉強維持住團結<br />\n而家冷卻左自然就內鬥返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988a7da1899729b68bc6fd9e0eb8030150d8f984","tid":2274313,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f4fb99ad18dc51979ef61f96d70a19df629dcbc","tid":2274313,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"推下呢d post"},{"pid":"d2bb13be28926cc73501c39ee4842ffe85c9a115","tid":2274313,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:54:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbd9f0472c77b89a137eb72bbc33b9425f0d8f03","tid":2274313,"uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d2bb13be28926cc73501c39ee4842ffe85c9a115","tid":2274313,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86b7adac38895cc00115037fad566ec5d8c82482","tid":2274313,"uid":121058,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"都on9既 依家係邊緣化緊認同民主黨/反侵既黃絲<br />\n成個時事台都係愛侵力<br />\n黃絲一定要支持侵？hocc唔係黃？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:54:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"咪就係,家下撐登果班KOL/左膠好多都撐飯民留任,<br />\n一早已經俾人覺得佢地係仆街"},{"pid":"1b9750163a2442f024a9ee6a64a2495e85611596","tid":2274313,"uid":69473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378acfa066864eae76516e6406bdcfc1ddb81b4d","tid":2274313,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:57:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ead97fb56075db56938b9375d18e8cb2a7031b57","tid":2274313,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"well said"},{"pid":"33285f1bb985f8d293ab28813443399d9df2bcdb","tid":2274313,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"709c4a9b8c3aa86fd1d12f714fbdb11e79e69a27","tid":2274313,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7fcdfa40235e112738897a6c6f379c273a0a0c","tid":2274313,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04241940b20494b5ff0dab9084d664f1126688e3","tid":2274313,"uid":303110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56128413dbf8535b1796201fdd06ca2f9066ae17","tid":2274313,"uid":316612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"總之黃營起爭議，就一定係五毛帶風向，大家收聲。直觀結果就係泛民永續議席、概得利益者繼續食饅頭。其實呢類講法已經冇晒市場，真係不值一駁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7977ccbdc02c125b44f64401e29596a3285565b","tid":2274313,"uid":215501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:37:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲post就推唔起"},{"pid":"618c202656af671a4066a9c4e70065b0661c9d33","tid":2274313,"uid":174502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"咁多post侵粉前cctoy後 都知乜事<br />\n唔講了 怕俾人話屈毛<br />\n利申 未fc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"27c5a779e839085ebb6ea149154658aef6c2f5b4","tid":2274313,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"愛回家醜化黃色經濟圈，抵制TVB團隊半個鐘內迅速反擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2274540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2274540</a><br />\n- 分